To say I’m excited about the upcoming @tandemcollectiveglobal read along for 𝗧𝗵𝗲 𝗟𝗮𝘀𝘁 𝗥𝗲𝘂𝗻𝗶𝗼𝗻 is an absolute understatement.

@kaytenunn2 is one of my favourite authors and when I saw this was happening I just had to be apart of it!

Starting on Monday, we’ll be reading this new release that follows five women who come together at a New Year’s Eve party after decades apart. Nunn does inter-generational stories so well - and I’m eager to read about the women who served in WW11 Burma!

I’ve tagged my fellow read along buddies, so be sure to check out their reviews and thoughts as we read.

